Tired of sorting pictures ?
Good news! Your camera stores date information in the picture file.
Based on this, this quick-and-dirty script moves every pictures from a directory
to another, but sorted by date. When matching a picture shot on May, the 1rst 2010,
the script will create a 2010/05/01 directory tree and store the picture in it.
Usage:
picture_sort directory_containing_unsorted_picture directory_to_sort_pictures

